            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Leviticus 13:1",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".) The reason for this is probably that Moses was designed by God as the great law-giver and teacher of the priesthood as well as of the laity.",
            "children": []
